    <id>https://training.galaxyproject.org/training-material/topics/microbiome/tutorials/metatranscriptomics/faqs/vsearch.html</id>
    <updated>2022-02-28T15:26:33+00:00</updated>
    <category term="new faq"/>
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;In the metatranscriptomics data, duplicated reads are expected. And to keep the integrity of the sample, we would like to retain the reverse reads.&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
