    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Currently, that is one of its limitations. However, Galaxy offers a workflow within workflow feature which can help process multiple files at the same time and this output can be combined into one using the &lt;code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"&gt;MT2MQ&lt;/code&gt; tool.&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
